---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString();
---

<Layout
  metadata={{
    title: 'Application & Data Security',
    description: 'How we protect your data: hosting, encryption, access controls, and operational practices.',
  }}
>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Application &amp; Data Security</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </section>

  <section class="prose prose-invert max-w-4xl">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Security is built into our product and operations. We combine platform controls with best practices to protect customer data.</p>

    <h2>Hosting &amp; infrastructure</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Hosted on reputable cloud providers with physical and network safeguards.</li>
      <li>Segregated environments for staging and production.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data protection</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Encryption in transit (TLS) and at rest for stored data.</li>
      <li>Least-privilege access to production systems.</li>
      <li>Backups and disaster recovery procedures.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Access &amp; authentication</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-factor authentication for administrative access.</li>
      <li>Role-based access controls; regular permission reviews.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Application security</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Dependency management and vulnerability scanning.</li>
      <li>Change management and code reviews for critical paths.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Incident response</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Documented incident response plan with defined SLAs and communication steps.</li>
      <li>Post-incident review and corrective actions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Privacy &amp; compliance</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>GDPR/CCPA-aligned practices where applicable.</li>
      <li>Data Processing Addendum available on request.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Subprocessors</h2>
    <p>We engage select providers to deliver the service (e.g., WhatsApp BSPs, hosting, analytics). A current list is available on request and will be published on our website.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For security inquiries or to report a vulnerability, email <a href="mailto:security@taprebook.com">security@taprebook.com</a>.</p>

    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 mt-8">This page is informational and will evolve as our controls mature.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

